title: Kieler Sprosse
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Salad bar, Take-out, Bakery, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Meat is only offered on Thursday; other days are veg. Opened Nov 2015 an all organic bistro offering breakfast, bagels, coffee, cake, gluten-free dishes, and daily changing lunch items. Has soy and oat milk, vegan baked goods.
